dcterms:description: The QM9 dataset contains a diverse set of organic molecules, specifically 133,885 organic molecules in equilibrium with up to 9 heavy atoms of four different types: C, O, N, and F. It provides the SMILES representation of the relaxed molecules, their geometric configurations, and 19 physical and chemical properties.
dcterms:title: QM9 dataset

dcterms:description: Mordred is a molecular descriptor calculator that generates knowledge-based vector representations of molecules based on their SMILES representation, providing 1826 physical and chemical features.
